{"tid":1964583,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英財相指約翰遜病情正改善　能於病床上坐起身","createTime":"2020-04-09T02:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T03:35:42.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"616bfed89a40394c1804977f7f6072fc4a541717","tid":1964583,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T02:29:45.000Z","msg":"確診感染武漢肺炎的英國首相約翰遜，繼續在深切治療部留醫。<br />\n<br />\n財相辛偉誠主持抗疫記者會時說，約翰遜的病情正在改善，已經能夠在病床上坐起身。辛偉誠又宣布一系列總值7億5千萬英鎊的措施，協助陷入困境的慈善團體，渡過疫情難關。他不願意猜測英國幾時可以解除目前各項封鎖措施，強調所有決定取決於科學數據。<br />\n<br />\n出席記者會的國防部科學顧問說，新確診個案的增速，並非失控。醫療官員就說，住院數據反映疫情出現首次平穩跡象，但強調不是自滿的時候，假如民眾不遵守保持社交距離的指引，病毒將再次快速傳播。<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1519688_1_20200409015022.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1519688_1_20200409015022.jpg&h=b4816bd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1519688-20200409.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1519688-20200409.htm&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbsbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=2b3580f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1519688-20200409.htm&h=0192990b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1519688-20200409.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e7742de32cce5ffe5de82680b74e0516628f2fa5","tid":1964583,"uid":259813,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T02:30:39.000Z","msg":"即係之前病到起唔到身？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef1601804a6c4164cbc336f87ddaf7d4227e907","tid":1964583,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T02:52:43.000Z","msg":"莊漢生病情正改善 能呼吸"},{"pid":"ebe0fb1ad509b83fa5499875d419a2ef56c5499a","tid":1964583,"uid":82068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T02:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eserv